Toh abhi aate hi ek baar aap please woh share kar dijiyega sir, thik hai sir?

Executive: Thik hai sir, thik hai sir. Thank you. Thank you sir.

Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Ha ha ha ha.
Customer: Thik hai sir, thik hai sir. Thik hai okay thik hai.
